content.text: *English:* National Anthem of the Kyrgyz Republic

page_title.text: National Anthem of the Kyrgyz Republic

items.text: The **[[LINK|lang_en|National_Anthem|National Anthem]] of the [[LINK|lang_en|Kyrgyz_Republic|Kyrgyz Republic]]** ( [[LINK|lang_en|Kyrgyz_language|Kyrgyz]] : Кыргыз Республикасынын Мамлекеттик Гимни, [[LINK|lang_en|Common_Turkic_alphabet|translit.]] : Qırğız Respublikasının Mamlekettik Gimni, قىرعىز رەسپۇبلىكاسىنىن ماملەكەتتىك گىمنى; [[LINK|lang_en|Russian_language|Russian]] : Государственный гимн Кыргызской Республики, *Gosudarstvennyj gimn Kyrgyzskoj Respubliki* ) was adopted on 18 December 1992 by a resolution of the [[LINK|lang_en|Supreme_Council_of_Kyrgyzstan|Supreme Council of Kyrgyzstan]] (Jogorku Kenesh).
The music was composed by Nasyr Davlesov and Kalyi Moldobasanov, and the words were written by Djamil Sadykov and Eshmambet Kuluev.

content.text: Are equal to the soul of our people.
Have lived in and kept the [[LINK|lang_en|Ala-Too|Ala-Too]].
*Your own fate is in your hands!*
Completed and gave us the clasp to nature.
We acquired an accord of harmony
*Your own fate is in your hands!*
Our hopes and aspirations have been fulfilled,
Our people wave the [[LINK|lang_en|Flag_of_Kyrgyzstan|flag of freedom]].
The tradition of our fathers came to us,
Let generations keep our holy heritage.
Извечно народ наш для дружбы открыт,
Единство и дружбу он в сердце хранит.
Izvečno narod naš dlja družby otkryt,
Jedinstvo i družbu on v serdce hranit.
Our eternal people are open to friendship,
Unity and friendship are kept in our hearts.
The land of [[LINK|lang_en|Kyrgyzstan|Kyrgyzstan]], our native state
The rays with consent have illuminated.
Dreams of the people came true,
And [[LINK|lang_en|Flag_of_Kyrgyzstan|the flag of liberty]] is over us.
The heritage of our fathers we will
Pass to our sons for the benefit of people.
